Package: peruflorads43
Title: Peruvian protected flora and fauna
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Paul Efren",
           family = "Santos Andrade",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "paulefrens@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6635-0375"))) 
Description: Provides access to the lists of flora and fauna protected by different laws in Peru.  The user supplies plant taxonomic names and the package returns the protected species information.
